#

Crispy Skin Roast Chicken with Garlic Mashed Potatoes

105 min
$15
700 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

dairy

Dietary Tags:

gluten-free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main CourseSide Dish

Tags:

chickenpotatoesroastedcomfort food

Description

Perfectly roasted chicken with crispy skin served alongside creamy garlic mashed potatoes for a hearty meal.

Ingredients

  • whole chicken: 1 (about 4 lbs)
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: 1 tablespoon
  • black pepper: 1 teaspoon
  • garlic: 4 cloves
  • potatoes: 2 lbs
  • butter: 4 tablespoons
  • milk: 1/2 cup
  • chives (optional): 2 tablespoons
